Feature based methods including topic modeling with LDA, TF-IDF and N-grams, were fed to a Logistic Regression classifier. In the LSTM architecture, we used {{2111.13611_FO0076||FO}} dimensional GloVe embeddings with a vocabulary size of {{2111.13611_FO0077||FO}}, and a {{2111.13611_FO0078||FO}} dimensional hidden state for LSTM.